### Test API Account System - HSO NEW
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### 1. Đăng ký tài khoản mới
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "test@hsonew.com",
  "phone": "0123456789"
}

### 2. Đăng nhập
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Đăng nhập bằng email
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test@hsonew.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. Lấy thông tin tài khoản (thay {id} bằng ID thực)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/account/1

### 5. Đổi mật khẩu (thay accountId bằng ID thực)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountId": 1,
  "oldPassword": "123456",
  "newPassword": "newpass123"
}

### 6. Test lỗi - Username đã tồn tại
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "123456",
  "email": "another@hsonew.com",
  "phone": "0987654321"
}

### 7. Test lỗi - Sai password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
} 